Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的心肝宝贝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可让我想死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么 你不喜欢咱家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国不是答应奴婢要做贵妃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么把奴婢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么把奴婢抬到这儿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 这郿坞比皇宫是好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郿坞是人间天堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郿坞虽好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是相国 相国毕竟不是天子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你既然已经答应了奴婢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就不该食言的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心肝啊 咱家跟你说实话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那天子是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子就是咱们养的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}掌上之物 徒有虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家是谁啊 咱家是尚父
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尚父是什么你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尚父他是天子的主子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是天子的爹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心肝啊 你与其伺候那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徒有虚名的天子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倒不如伺候伺候天子他爹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你 你弄疼我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好好 弄疼你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宝贝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我向你赔罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以后你就住在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家要让你享尽天下至乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家要把天下所有的珍奇宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全都送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事呢 你给我唱个小曲儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知相国想听什么曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我最爱听那个那个 那个叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暖玉温香抱满怀 离魂到天外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这句我是最爱听了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奴婢这就去卸妆更衣准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更衣 更衣好 更衣 更衣好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过你可要快着点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来人哪 在 伺候小姐更衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了兴汉灭贼非如此不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}女儿 我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}求你为大汉献身哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心肝宝贝啊 快着点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家都等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军为何独坐在此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此刻上朝也太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不是上朝 我想见貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}见貂蝉 干吗坐这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这儿离貂蝉近一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恕老夫直言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉根本就不在皇宫里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那她在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 你还不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨夜初更时分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉就被抬进了郿坞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伺候相国大人去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么 郿坞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老夫担心哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}担心什么 快说你担心什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老夫担心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然貂蝉被抬进了郿坞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恐怕就上了相国的凤榻牙床了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 我不信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我万万不信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国他亲口跟我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是给天子做贵妃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国不但跟将军这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟百官也是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国怎么能够堂堂正正地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把貂蝉抬走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这事让人万难相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过刚才我碰上了内廷侍奉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他亲口跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天夜里就是他亲手提着灯笼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把貂蝉坐的宫轿引入郿坞的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}董卓这个老禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小女本该是将军的爱妻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可相国却借着天子的名义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}强占了将军的爱妻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种事也确实近乎禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万一传扬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国自然不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可将军你怎么做人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 你要干什么去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么那么早就起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来来来 来来来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么了这是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再躺一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国 相国您该早朝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看看 你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都不急你急什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来来来来来 再躺一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 我去梳妆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}梳妆 梳妆好 梳妆好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心肝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心肝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:14:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我离不开你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这里不是说话的地方 快走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 我要带你走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先 你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我来请相国上朝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是这样 好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你暂且到宫外等候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}记住 今后没有我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不许到我的寝宫来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先 奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何如此惊慌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不急 慢慢说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国他霸占了貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那貂蝉与你有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下早就和貂蝉定情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相约白头到老 生死与共
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可义父
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}义父他却以给天子立妃为名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把貂蝉接到郿坞来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先哪 奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你已经贵为公侯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么样的女人没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}区区一个貂蝉值什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何至于如此伤感哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 她是我的命根子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我离不开她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先哪 恕我斗胆问一句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果你得不到貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你将会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我绝不甘休
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣斗胆建言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是把那貂蝉赏还给吕布吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此刻天下未定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国仍需将士用命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国欲夺天下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必须笼络住吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让他驰骋疆场 攻城拔寨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有这样相国才能成就大业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他要什么咱家都可以给他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唯独这个貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要知道貂蝉是人间极品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家舍不得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请相国斟酌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万一吕布怒而悖反
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}甚至投奔袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与我们为敌的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可就大事去也啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是吕布的义父
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我对他不薄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他对我也是忠心耿耿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他怎会因此女而悖我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢问相国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丁原是怎么死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国你只用了一匹赤兔马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就收得吕布前来归顺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不但如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布居然为了这匹赤兔马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟亲手杀了自己的义父丁原
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么现在吕布为了貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又会做出何等事来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉与赤兔马相比孰重孰轻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大业与一个粉黛尤物相比
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何者当取 何者当弃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可真是个仙人儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家是越看越爱看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来来来来来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:21:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宝贝 来来来来来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心肝啊 来来来来来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家今天啊跟你说个事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽说吕布是我的义子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是天下第一勇夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我思来想去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然他对你是这样地放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就成人之美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把你赏给他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们两个在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:21:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不但是郎才女貌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是情投意和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将来定然是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如鱼得水 如胶似漆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国 奴婢没做错什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.47,0:22:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天相国还对奴婢宠爱有加
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.14,0:22:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是今天却要将奴婢转送给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奴婢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奴婢还不如相国
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喜欢的一个物件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.32,0:22:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这说的什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 我就是想提出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.06,0:23:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和你商量商量嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}本以为相国是真心对奴婢好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奴婢也愿意侍奉相国一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.68,0:23:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是相国
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却要将奴婢转送给一个下人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国 你还是赐奴婢一死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以免侮辱了相国之尊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的心肝 你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我啊 我跟你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实我呀也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.31,0:23:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从心里头不愿意放你走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.11,0:23:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的 我舍不得你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.15,0:24:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来来来 来 宝贝 来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.86,0:24:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宝贝啊 咱家还想跟你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.60,0:24:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白头到老 富贵终生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.57,0:24:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.37,0:24:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我怎么能骗你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.38,0:24:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.88,0:24:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何要将我许配给吕将军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.41,0:24:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫不是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.98,0:24:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫不是你怕他不成
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.75,0:24:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 我怕他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.82,0:24:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他是我干儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.03,0:24:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然不怕 还要将我许配给他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.60,0:24:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当今天下谁人不知谁人不晓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.10,0:24:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连天子都要敬让你三分
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.57,0:24:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是你连自己的爱妾都留不住
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.91,0:24:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这要是传出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.74,0:25:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外面的人会怎么想你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.51,0:25:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您岂不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.68,0:25:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成了公卿大臣的笑柄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.69,0:25:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 说得对 咱家糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.96,0:25:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.19,0:25:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家绝不把你让给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.87,0:25:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家和你永不分离
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.07,0:25:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国 到时辰该上朝了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.44,0:25:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上朝 这
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.58,0:25:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 上朝 上朝
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.45,0:25:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国赴朝 众军护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.73,0:25:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.17,0:26:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先 随义父走走
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.68,0:26:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.15,0:26:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先啊 义父待你如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.32,0:26:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}义父待我情意深重 恩同再造
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.06,0:26:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}记着
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.43,0:26:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家早晚要改朝换代即大位
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.50,0:26:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个时候咱家定和你共享天下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.67,0:26:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有 咱家膝下无子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.50,0:26:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是我的亲儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.87,0:26:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家即位之后
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.74,0:26:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一件事就是要立你为太子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.18,0:26:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家百年之后
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.58,0:26:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下就是你的 大位就是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.19,0:26:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢义父
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.26,0:26:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们父子俩 你说你谢什么谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.70,0:27:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.30,0:27:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在即位之前咱家得抬举抬举你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.80,0:27:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.61,0:27:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷中大将军这个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.71,0:27:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直是空缺待补
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.31,0:27:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家早就有意于你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.91,0:27:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是恐怕西凉军众将不服
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.15,0:27:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特别是李傕 郭汜二将
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.12,0:27:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们说你年轻气盛不堪大任
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.95,0:27:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都要和你争这个大将军的位置啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.62,0:27:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将不敢相争
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.89,0:27:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家决定
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.63,0:27:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜你为朝廷的大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.57,0:27:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}统管天下所有兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.50,0:27:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢义父大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.24,0:27:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布肝脑涂地难以回报
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.78,0:27:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快起来 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.99,0:27:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.69,0:27:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你 你还有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.90,0:28:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.77,0:28:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.70,0:28:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有就好 没有就好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.38,0:28:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀相国
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.48,0:28:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冀州牧韩馥近日与袁绍交恶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.49,0:28:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他上表朝廷要求天子下诏讨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.69,0:28:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊 那就赐他一诏
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.33,0:28:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}着他奉诏剿灭袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.23,0:28:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他如是胜了咱家就再赐他
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.40,0:28:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再赐他三郡之地
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.87,0:28:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.18,0:28:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上月以来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.61,0:28:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操在青 兖二州
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.98,0:29:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连续剿灭了五路黄巾乱军
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.02,0:29:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得降卒二十余万
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.06,0:29:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}号称青州兵 声势益大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.46,0:29:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个曹阿瞒是越发了得了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.57,0:29:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家得想法子收拢他才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.94,0:29:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣还有一事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.94,0:29:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿只管说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.38,0:29:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自开春以来中原一直大旱
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.15,0:29:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}近日几个州已经是易子相食
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.99,0:29:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好几个州郡都上书
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.59,0:29:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要求朝廷拨粮相救
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.97,0:29:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家的粮食还不够吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.87,0:29:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪里有粮食给他们哪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.77,0:29:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那朝廷要是不拨
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.71,0:29:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坐视不顾的话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.14,0:30:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恐怕要有几十万灾民丧生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.15,0:30:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这你怕什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.82,0:30:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这千百年来 这七灾八难的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.29,0:30:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是也都没断过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.66,0:30:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是怎么着了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.69,0:30:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这人丁是越来越兴旺了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.23,0:30:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人是越来越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.83,0:30:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黔首百姓 贱着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.94,0:30:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}启奏相国
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.58,0:30:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}百姓的口粮虽然可以不管
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.18,0:30:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是谷种必须要予以相济啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.32,0:30:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则明年春天
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.26,0:30:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}粮农们没有谷种播种
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.36,0:30:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}则是全年无收
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.59,0:30:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷的税赋也就断了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.40,0:30:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那谷种哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.40,0:30:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那谷种都哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.74,0:31:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奄奄一息的饥民什么都会吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.47,0:31:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁叫他把谷种都给吃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.64,0:31:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是饥不择食
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.68,0:31:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣斗胆启奏相国
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.02,0:31:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郿坞囤有百万石粮草
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.12,0:31:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}足够二十年食用
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.03,0:31:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请相国为天下百姓着想
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.10,0:31:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拨出十分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.13,0:31:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以供粮农做谷种
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.20,0:31:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等到明年秋收以后
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.64,0:31:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令他们加倍偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.67,0:31:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你等会儿 等等 等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.04,0:31:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁说我们郿坞里头
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.61,0:31:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}存着百万石粮草啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.21,0:31:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁说的 纯属胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.78,0:31:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.63,0:31:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要不信的话
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.03,0:31:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可以问问奉先嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.53,0:32:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他是朝廷的大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.20,0:32:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他应该知道详情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.90,0:32:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是 奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.44,0:32:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.41,0:32:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.05,0:32:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吁
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.89,0:32:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.36,0:32:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国差我前来 闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.63,0:32:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.40,0:33:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.71,0:33:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.82,0:33:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉 我日日夜夜都在想你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.02,0:33:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.30,0:33:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.70,0:33:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉已经
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.71,0:33:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.21,0:33:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉之所以忍辱偷生地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.65,0:34:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是为了见将军最后一面
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.19,0:34:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天貂蝉终于见着将军你了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.06,0:34:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉的心愿已了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.87,0:34:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就让貂蝉来生再侍奉将军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.58,0:34:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.68,0:34:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}若你死了我怎么活
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.35,0:34:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果不能和将军在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.79,0:34:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉活着又有什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.63,0:34:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军就 就让貂蝉死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.13,0:35:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 我要与你同生共死
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.58,0:35:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉 我一定会把你夺回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.89,0:35:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军说的是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.83,0:35:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.73,0:35:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请让我慢慢想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.22,0:35:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布可曾来过
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.75,0:35:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀相国 吕将军刚进去不久
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.96,0:36:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.17,0:36:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果我们可以永远都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.80,0:36:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}该多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.48,0:36:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}逆子 你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.18,0:36:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}逆子 你竟敢调戏咱家小妾
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.89,0:36:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.72,0:36:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.99,0:36:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我饶不了你 你这个逆子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.96,0:37:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你 逆子 忤逆 我饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.78,0:37:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}逆子 逆子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.45,0:37:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}逆子 我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.36,0:37:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悖君之贼 悖君之贼
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.40,0:37:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}气死我了 气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.88,0:37:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奴婢正在观鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.05,0:37:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然 突然吕将军出现
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.45,0:37:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奴婢躲闪不及
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.59,0:38:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军抱着奴婢就是不放
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.73,0:38:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国 你可要为奴婢做主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.97,0:38:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布忤逆 无耻之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.65,0:38:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家一定饶不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.45,0:38:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让你受惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.85,0:38:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奴婢当时只想投湖自尽
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.56,0:38:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以免辱没了相国之声
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.26,0:38:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是吕将军把奴婢死死的抱住
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.74,0:38:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幸亏相国及时赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.55,0:39:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心肝 咱 咱不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.25,0:39:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱不怕 来 不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.22,0:39:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱家给你做主
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.12,0:39:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一定饶不了那厮
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.89,0:39:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫哭 咱不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.40,0:39:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣王允拜见相国
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.60,0:39:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}王允啊 你都知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.14,0:39:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣刚才见吕布匆匆忙忙奔命
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.67,0:39:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老夫也就猜测出一二了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.68,0:39:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布忤逆 无耻之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.72,0:39:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然干出这种
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.15,0:39:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卑鄙无耻的勾当来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.49,0:39:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我呀 要把他正法
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.66,0:39:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.32,0:39:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老臣敢请相国借一步说话
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.34,0:39:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么着
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.91,0:40:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老臣琢磨着
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.78,0:40:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}事情既然已经做下了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.11,0:40:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布当然是罪不可赦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.18,0:40:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但吕布是相国的义子爱将
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.45,0:40:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}凤仪亭之事如果传扬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.33,0:40:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这必然百官沸然 天下失笑
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.60,0:40:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也大损相国的威严哪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.73,0:40:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再者说
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.03,0:40:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布英勇无双 足堪大任
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.37,0:40:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如斩了吕布就如同自断臂膀
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.68,0:40:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因小失大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.75,0:40:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你说怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.88,0:40:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与其治吕布之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.02,0:40:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如赐他一条生路
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.95,0:40:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}化祸为福
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.29,0:40:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么个化祸为福
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.29,0:40:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国顺水推舟
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.56,0:40:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将小女貂蝉赐给他
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.73,0:40:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.47,0:40:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.60,0:41:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把小女貂蝉赐给他 以安其心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.81,0:41:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样以后吕布必然感恩戴德
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.04,0:41:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生生死死忠于相国
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.21,0:41:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如是皆大欢喜
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.05,0:41:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}王司徒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.52,0:41:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.69,0:41:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这事咱家也想过
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.26,0:41:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是咱家同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.83,0:41:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那爱姬不同意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.74,0:41:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣是貂蝉的义父
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.87,0:41:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣可令她从命
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.89,0:41:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也罢 你去和她说说试试
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.66,0:41:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.56,0:42:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小女拜见义父
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.90,0:42:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}死丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.73,0:42:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看你给相国惹下多少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.84,0:42:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给相国父子之间
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.07,0:42:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惹下多少误会
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.38,0:42:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听着 即刻更衣 随老父离去
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.02,0:42:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}义父要带我去哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.49,0:42:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我带你到吕布将军处谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.13,0:42:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从今往后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.46,0:42:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就伺候吕将军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.57,0:42:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你个死丫头 你听见没有
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.70,0:42:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是你父 你敢违抗父命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.88,0:42:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}义父 我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.65,0:42:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你放肆
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.75,0:42:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国 我们来生再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.13,0:43:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉 貂蝉哪 我的心肝哪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.96,0:43:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.83,0:43:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么能这样 貂蝉哪 心肝 相国
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.90,0:43:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉哪 心肝 相国
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.13,0:43:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的宝贝啊 相国
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.64,0:43:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用管她 让她死好了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.31,0:43:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种无情无义
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.34,0:43:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无忠无孝的死丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.54,0:43:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}留她何用
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.41,0:43:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}住口 都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.71,0:43:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是想害死咱家爱姬呀
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.25,0:43:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.42,0:43:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老臣可是处处为相国着想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.12,0:43:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滚
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.09,0:43:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相国啊 滚
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.29,0:43:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再不滚我劈了你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.23,0:43:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是是是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.86,0:43:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太医 我的心肝啊
